fers star health assure insurance policy, star cancer care platinum insurance policy, senior citizens health insurance policy, and star cardiac care insurance policy \u0096 platinum, as well as star group OPD care insurance product. The company offers its products through web aggregators, digital channels, agency channels, corporate agents, brokers, point of salesperson, insurance marketing firms, and various other channels. Star Health and Allied Insurance Company was incorporated in 2005 and is based in Chennai, India."}}